		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黑影进行横、纵、旋3段攻击，横纵攻击均造成<span color="#b8b8b8">20%</span><span>伤害，旋转造成4段</span><span color="#b8b8b8">8%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="927" width="434" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黑影高跃，瞄准蕈兽，然后落地造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害。若命中「替身忍犬」，则自身将受到</span><span color="#ff9999">75%</span><span>伤害并瘫痪一小会。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蕈兽%B7帽子刀子狗子.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="170">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蕈兽%B7帽子刀子狗子.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="841">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黑影在蕈兽处留下「替身忍犬」，然后传送开；一段时间后传送回来。「替身忍犬」引爆造成<span color="#ff9999">66.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
