			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黑影使用嘴部咬住刀，转身放出3道雷刃造成<span color="#ffacff">150%,37.5%,15%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
